                        <button class="tab" data-tab="resonance">Rezonans</button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content active" id="equation">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Majburiy tebranish tenglamasi:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$m\ddot{x} + \gamma\dot{x} + kx = F_0\cos(\omega_e t)$$
                        </div>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-dim);">
                            Bu yerda: m - massa, Œ≥ - ishqalanish, k - bikrlik, F‚ÇÄ - tashqi kuch amplitudasi, œâ‚Çë - haydovchi chastota
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="solution">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Steady-state yechim:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$x(t) = A\cos(\omega_e t - \phi)$$
                        </div>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Amplituda:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$A = \frac{F_0/m}{\sqrt{(\omega_0^2 - \omega_e^2)^2 + (\gamma\omega_e)^2}}$$
                        </div>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Faza kechikishi:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$\tan\phi = \frac{\gamma\omega_e}{\omega_0^2 - \omega_e^2}$$
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tab-content" id="resonance">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Rezonans chastota:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$\omega_{res} = \sqrt{\omega_0^2 - \frac{\gamma^2}{2}}$$
                        </div>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Maksimal amplituda:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$A_{max} = \frac{F_0}{m\gamma\omega_{res}}$$
                        </div>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Q-faktor:</p>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            $$Q = \frac{\omega_0}{\gamma}$$
                        </div>
                        <div class="info-box">
                            <p><strong>Rezonans:</strong> œâ‚Çë ‚âà œâ‚ÇÄ bo'lganda amplituda maksimal bo'ladi</p>
                            <p><strong>Q-faktor:</strong> Rezonans "o'tkirligi"ni bildiradi</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Info -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-title">‚ÑπÔ∏è Ma'lumot</div>
                    <div class="info-box">
                        <p><strong>Transient:</strong> Boshlang'ich jarayon, so'nib boruvchi tebranish</p>
                        <p><strong>Steady State:</strong> Barqaror holat, doimiy amplituda</p>
                        <p><strong>Lissajous:</strong> Fazoviy trajektoriya, tizim holatini ko'rsatadi</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
